What you need to know:

The much-changed Gunners, who have won the competition a record 14 times, fell behind midway through the first half against their energetic opponentsMikel Arteta, who won the FA Cup in August in his first season as Arsenal boss, said he was "really sad" to exit the competitionSouthampton, the 1976 FA Cup winners, reaped the reward their positive approach deserved in the 24th minute